      <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sup Intro</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">I'll help you complete the Supervisor Transfer test call. I'll provide instructions step by step. OK?</Data></Cell></Row>
      <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sup Instructions</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">When you need to transfer:
1) Ask in chat first
2) Give CCM time to check
3) When CCM says ok - let caller know you are transferring</Data></Cell></Row>
      <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sup Transfer</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">1. Click Transfer in CC
