      <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sup Disposition</Data></Cell><Cell ss:StyleID="Wrap"><Data ss:Type="String">Click cancel (red phone), disposition as Test/Training.
Then disposition in Call Corp.</Data></Cell></Row>
      <Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Sup Retry</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Transfer was not successful. Review steps and let me know when ready.</Data></Cell></Row>
